question: Which university is located in Tromsø, Norway?
true_answer: UiT Norges arktiske universitet (UiT The Arctic University of Norway).
asked_question_translated: Která univerzita se nachází v norském Tromsø?
answer: V norském Tromsø se nachází Univerzita v Tromsø (UiT - Norges arktiske universitet).
answer_translated_eng: V norském Tromsø se nachází Univerzita v Tromsø (UiT - The Arctic University of Norway).
